name: Functus playing drums
description:
This was a dream I had.

The percussionist would be hanging like this playing their sets.

That's also the way functus will move around in the future.

what are functus? you may ask.

Functus are the evolution of Sapiens.

Since machines can think better than a human,
our species no longer need to be sapiens.

Our DNA can be minted into a new function.

Homo Functus,
~ soon in a space colony near you.
